         <abstract id="aspace_667c8043d71755c4a7b45325e63c0d32">Largely writings of Lee De Forest including typescripts of his diary, of his published autobiography, and of an article on turbines. The small amount of his correspondence includes a series of letters to Jessica Wallace Millar.</abstract>
